# Structure: ZS_EMPLOYEE_DISPLAY

## Description
This structure is used for displaying employee details along with a calculated field for years of experience.

## Fields

| Field Name     | Data Element | Description               |
|----------------|--------------|---------------------------|
| EMP_ID         | ZDE_EID      | Employee ID               |
| NAME           | ZDE_NAME     | Employee Name             |
| DEPT           | ZDE_DEPT     | Department                |
| DOJ            | ZDE_DOJ      | Date of Joining           |
| YEARS_OF_EXP   | ZDE_YEXP     | Years of Experience       |

## Use Case
This structure is commonly used in:
- ALV reports
- Output views
- Program calculations (YEARS_OF_EXP can be derived from DOJ)

